{"title":"战斗吧，朋友","authors":["多乍·西立玛"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":8,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"战斗吧，朋友"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔老挝〕多乍·西立玛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战斗而死，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜过投降而生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了全国人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顽强地斗争！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的军队英勇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杀敌不留情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把侵犯阴谋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚决粉碎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战斗而死，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜过死在卧床上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要跪着乞求"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——群魔发善心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要幻想、等待"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——和平会降临。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干涉、劫掠……，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"魔鬼们把坏事做尽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战斗而死，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜过苟且偷安。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朋友啊，起来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把群魔驱逐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们期待的统一，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终久要实现。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最后胜利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更向我们临近。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}